reviews.review_text: I was there!  My first DD Show. The above 'show' appears to be both the early and late show. The early set ending in UJB was my show, after which the gym was emptied for the separate-ticket late show.  BTW, ticket cost was $2 and was the second highest priced ticket for a SUSB show that I paid in my 4 years there.  (Who doing Tommy cost $5). Getting Jerry and Mickey with both the GD and NRPS certainly cemented the Jer Bear into my psychedelically infused mind.  They were a tad sloppy on a couple tunes like anyone cared.  Final Viola Lee ever.
